      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 py-2">What is structured data and why does my Swansea business need it?</summary>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-2">Structured data is code added to your website that helps search engines understand your content. For Swansea businesses, LocalBusiness schema tells Google your address, opening hours, and service area. This can trigger rich results like star ratings, FAQs, and business details directly in search results, increasing your click-through rate.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 py-2">How much does technical SEO cost in Swansea?</summary>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-2">Technical SEO services in Swansea typically range from a one-off audit starting at around £500 to ongoing monthly retainers from £300 to £1,500 depending on the scope. Visit our <a href="/seo-pricing-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline">pricing page</a> for a full breakdown of packages suited to Swansea businesses of different sizes.</p>
