    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 py-2">Can I do technical SEO myself or do I need an expert?</summary>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-2">Basic technical SEO tasks like installing an SSL certificate or compressing images can be handled in-house. However, issues like crawl budget management, JavaScript rendering, canonical tag conflicts, and server-side performance tuning require specialist knowledge and tools. Most Swansea businesses benefit from at least an initial professional audit to identify and prioritise the issues that matter most.</p>
